title: Gay - Hot Times in Little Havana (Kristen Bjorn)
description:
Hot Times in Little Havana follows the exploits of a forlorn lover in search of his long-lost mate, taking him from the despair of Cuba to the cornucopia of carnal delights 90 miles to the north in the decadent states. Director Kristen Bjorn populates this sensuous love story with 19 hot guys from Cuba, Puerto Rico, Columbia, Brazil and Argentina. Bjorn once again creates a lush video that rocks in every way. His ability to create a symphony of well-choreographed sexual performances really shines.

Hot men--Hot times--Please seed!!
